            "Tulus is an Indonesian singer-songwriter who runs his own label, TulusCompany. He was introduced to Indonesia’s music scene in 2011 with a debut album titled in his mononym, Tulus. The album earned the top spot in Rolling Stone Indonesia’s January and February 2012 listings. Over the span of ten years, Tulus has put his name among the A-lister Indonesian singers. His works have been widely appreciated among audiences from various segments, both in Indonesia as well as abroad. Tulus with TulusCompany released 5 successful albums called Tulus, Gajah, Monokrom, Langsung dari Konser Monokrom Jakarta (Live), and Manusia with line of songs that hit Indonesian charts, such as “Sewindu,” “Gajah,” “Pamit”, “Adaptasi” and “Hati-hati di Jalan”. All of his achievements and awards are proof that Tulus is a successful singer who has managed to penetrate the competitive music industry in Indonesia. Among them are “The Best Album of The Year” in 2015 for Gajah and in 2018 for Monokrom by Anugerah Musik Indonesia. He was also awarded as \"The Best Urban Soloist\" in 2017 and 2019.",
